title: 12/18/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 12/18/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's game. Is Justin Herbert the real deal or is it still too early to tell? We also preview Conference Championship weekend in College Football. What would need to happen to shake up the Committee's current top 4 teams? We're joined by Former College Head Coach Rick Neuheisel, ESPN College Football Analyst Jesse Palmer, and the LA Times Columnist Bill Plaschke.
